text:
Tum thoda jaldi chale gye to tumhara toast nhi sunn paye....Over the years I developed a special weird bond with you..We connected over courses, mera there kamre me sona aur teri mithai kha jana and all other weird activities we did as a wing! You're very sensible and sensitive (which you don't let out). Tumhare subtle comments jinse tau ki roasting shuru ho jati thib and tum fir enjoy karte the, vo tedi smile jab bhi tu kuch double meaning bolta ya sochta hai , tumhari slider moaning bowling...sab iconic hai bhai.
Tumhari planning and constant efforts jisse tum chaapte ho inspire me a lot and kafi kuch seekha hai mene tujhse (Jo abhi implement karna baki hai :| ) I know you'll be really successful in your life and help a lot of people with your compassion...bass tumhare hero poses aur tedi smile bnaye rkhna IPS sir! Will meet you soon...and tumhare sath to ab hmesha hi rhenge. 
Cheers to the last win we had in Buchasia ka quiz! Thanks for all the experiences bro!
author: Priyanshu  Saxena
